        Creates a new set of entities.
        Parameters:
        entitySetId - The id of the entity set to write to.
        syncId - A time-uuid retrieved from data source api.
        entities - A map describe the entities to create. Each key will be used as the entity id and must be unique and stable across repeated integrations of data. If either constraint is violated then data may be overwritten or duplicated.
